{"tid":2348731,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[武肺] 再有捐血者確診 受血病人因自身病離世 醫生：血液感染可能性微乎其微","createTime":"2021-01-01T03:44:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T13:49:29.000Z","uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"636c8e2e31f0d4074e1e390db83a7be7d20c52cb","tid":2348731,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T03:44:45.000Z","msg":"有患者接受武肺病人捐出的血液後，翌日因自身疾病離世，引發公眾對武肺病毒會否經血液傳染的關注。血液及血液腫瘤科專科醫生區永仁表示，目前全球未有血液感染武肺的案例及醫學實證，意味可能性微乎其微；目前紅十字會為捐血者安排的篩查已足夠把關，公眾無須過慮。<br />\n<br />\n全部睇link <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201231/NMZYUYNKJJBJXBX3I7OJXAVSDM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0-xxZ81fIyDzDElmBDqzRod2K7c_Kr8vbehpcxOtAwtTlQ8atNd9sm08U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201231%2FNMZYUYNKJJBJXBX3I7OJXAVSDM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0-xxZ81fIyDzDElmBDqzRod2K7c_Kr8vbehpcxOtAwtTlQ8atNd9sm08U&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindhWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=a171c351\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201231%2FNMZYUYNKJJBJXBX3I7OJXAVSDM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0-xxZ81fIyDzDElmBDqzRod2K7c_Kr8vbehpcxOtAwtTlQ8atNd9sm08U&h=8bbf5c7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201231/NMZYUYNKJJBJXBX3I7OJXAVSDM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0-xxZ81fIyDzDElmBDqzRod2K7c_Kr8vbehpcxOtAwtTlQ8atNd9sm08U</a>"},{"pid":"c69598b38f30336fcd74404478f8d29cd4392773","tid":2348731,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T13:43:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>目前全球未有血液感染武肺的案例及醫學實證，意味可